Setting.Name: DnnjQueryPlugins
Setting.Help: If true, the dnn plugins used for panels and tabs will be loaded in addition to jQuery and jQueryUI.

Setting.Name: jQueryHoverIntent
Setting.Help: If true, the HoverIntent script used for tooltips will be loaded in addition to jQuery.

Setting.Name: jQueryUI
Setting.Help: If true, jQueryUI will be loaded in addition to jQuery.
